    .page-header
      %h1 Overview
    %p This describes the resources that make up the official KakiTube API v1. If you have any problems or requests please contact support.
    %p
      Our API is organized around REST. JSON will be returned in all responses from the API. All API access is over HTTPS, and accessed from the
      %mark kakitube.com/api/v1
      domain. All data is sent and received as JSON.
    .page-header
      %h1 Authentication
    %h3 Current Version
    %p By default, all requests receive the v1 version of the API
    %h3 Schema
    %p You authenticate to the KakiTube API by providing your API Access Token in the request. You can get your API key from your accountâ€™s settings page.
    %p Authentication to the API occurs via HTTP Header Authorization. Provide your API key as HTTP Header.
    .terminal
      %p
        $ curl -X GET -H "Access-Token: YourSecureRandomApiKey" http://kakitube.com/api/v1/movies/cold-eyes-korean-movie -I
      %p
        HTTP/1.1 200 OK
        %br/
        X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
        %br/
        X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
        %br/
        X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
        %br/
        Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
        %br/
        ETag: W/"c2e383f347f85be39df33a794c111817"
        %br/
        Cache-Control: max-age=0, private, must-revalidate
        %br/
        X-Request-Id: 37981503-d392-4dc5-9c45-951223cb4599
        %br/
        X-Runtime: 0.356851
        %br/
        Date: Thu, 21 May 2015 04:38:13 GMT
      %p
        []
    %p Blank fields are included as null instead of being omitted.
    %strong Failed Authentication
    .terminal
      %p HTTP/1.1 401 Unauthorized
    %h3 Parameters
    %p.text-warning Currently we only support for GET request to our Movies and TV Series listing. We planning to release other action method [PUT, PATCH, DESTROY] in future.
    %strong Get All Movies List
    .terminal
      %p
        $ curl -X GET -H "Access-Token: YourSecureRandomApiKey" http://kakitube.com/api/v1/movies -I
      %p
        HTTP/1.1 200 OK
    %strong Get All TV-Series List
    .terminal
      %p
        $ curl -X GET -H "Access-Token: YourSecureRandomApiKey" http://kakitube.com/api/v1/tv-series -I
      %p
        HTTP/1.1 200 OK
    %strong Get Movie Data
    .terminal
      %p
        $ curl -X GET -H "Access-Token: YourSecureRandomApiKey" http://kakitube.com/api/v1/movies/movie-title -I
      %p
        HTTP/1.1 200 OK
    %strong Get TV-Series Data
    .terminal
      %p
        $ curl -X GET -H "Access-Token: YourSecureRandomApiKey" http://kakitube.com/api/v1/tv-series/series-title -I
      %p
        HTTP/1.1 200 OK
    %strong Failed GET request data
    .terminal
      %p HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found
